eligibility_criteria.description:
Minimum age: 0 Years
Maximum age: 60 Years
This trial does not accept healthy volunteers.
Patients who have had a history of non-cutaneous malignancy in the previous 5 years are not eligible; exception: patients with history of non-melanoma skin cancer are eligible

The presence of a medical or psychiatric condition that, in the opinion of the
             investigator, makes the patient inappropriate for study inclusion.

Patients who are currently receiving other anti-cancer agents or radiation therapy
             are not eligible.
Prior cytotoxic chemotherapy or radiotherapy for this lymphoma
have not been treated with a taxane within six months of C1D1, AND
Patients with cervix cancer who have received any previous radiation or chemotherapy

outcome_measures.analysis_method: Induction: pre-infusion (0 hr) on Day 1 of Cycle 1; pre-infusion (within 5 hr prior to dose) on Day 1 on Cycles 2, 4; Post-induction: at treatment discontinuation (up to Month 24); 120 days and 1-2 years post-last dose (maximum up to 5 years) (infusion duration: 90 minutes) (1 cycle: 21 days)
outcome_measures.time_frame: Pre-infusion (0 hr) on Day 1 of Cycle 1 up to maximum 5 years. Detailed timeframe is given in outcome measure description.
